    "In particular, they expressed appreciation for how it made learning more meaningful, encouraged critical thinking, and enabled independent learning.",
    "However, the long response of the chatbot was also stated to be a limiting issue, besides dissatisfaction with some answers that the bot gave.",
    "Improvement through the iterative refinement process will, therefore, be one key means of optimizing learning outcomes from this tutor bot.",
    "In response to Research Question 1 (RQ1), the study demonstrates that structured prompts for the ChatGPT-powered tutor bot significantly enhance students' engagement and learning experiences.",
    "By adhering to these prompts, students were better positioned to focus on the intended learning objectives, thereby facilitating a more organized and guided learning process (Garg & Rajendran, 2024; Tassoti, 2024)."
